    "comment": "Rationale: Results section. \"Ultrastructural localization of Syt11 in rat hippocampal CA1 synapses by immunoelectron microscopy\"\n\n-Literal: \" We finally examined the ultrastructural distribution of Syt11 protein in rat hippocampus by immunogold EM (Fig. 6) ...In axon terminals, Syt11 signals were colocalized with presynaptic vesicles...\"\n\n22/2/2018 Pim\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Methods section: \"Electron microcopy\"\n\n-Literal. \"Ultrastructural subcellular localization of Syt11 in rat brains was examined using immuno-EM, as described previously (Paik et al., 2011). CA1 hippocampal sections of rat brains (60 lm; 8 weeks) were incubated for 2 h with goat anti-Syt11 antibodies (1:200) and rabbit anti-goat IgG 10 nm gold-conjugated (EMS, #25228, SUA) .....\"",
